folder: Coney Island Creek - West 20th Street - Brooklyn., NY
text:
Coney Island Creek, at the foot of West 20th Street, and viewing eastward to the Cropsey Ave. Bridge. This is a set of three views taken the same day.

May 17, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Coney Island Creek - West 20th Street - Brooklyn.
